	<longdescription>
		guish is a GUI creation and modification tool that can 
		be used to tie different programs together using XEmbed 
		protocol and the shell (or as standalone) to create 
		new programs, or to make simple GUIs.
	</longdescription>
	<use>
		<flag name="debug">Build with debugging support</flag>
		<flag name="embedded-control">Enable controlling embedded external programs through key-sequences</flag>
